## Erlang VM arguments for the PulseMesh fabric node.

## Node name and distribution cookie. Override in production.
-sname pulsemesh_fabric
-setcookie pulsemesh_dev_cookie

## Enable kernel poll for efficient socket handling.
+K true

## Reasonable process limit for a connection-fabric node.
+P 1048576

## Heartbeat between distributed nodes.
-kernel net_ticktime 30
